OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FVictims of the "horrendous" crime of
OL,7,Fstalking are to be given better
OL,8,Fprotection including the right to know
OL,9,Fthe identity of their online stalkers,
OL,10,Fthe Government has said.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,13,Fcommitted to using "every tool
OL,14,Favailable" to take power from abusers
OL,15,Fand hand it to victims.
OL,17,FThe changes come following a warning
OL,18,Fearlier this year from a group of
OL,19,Fwatchdogs who said police are failing
OL,20,Fto protect stalking victims in too
OL,21,Fmany cases.
