OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FAround one in seven people aged 16 and
OL,7,Fover in England and Wales have been a
OL,8,Fvictim of stalking at least once,
OL,9,Ffigures suggest.
OL,11,FNew "right to know" statutory guidance
OL,12,Fis aimed at ensuring police can
OL,13,Freassure those being stalked that they
OL,14,Fwill be told the identity of an online
OL,15,Fstalker at the earliest opportunity.
