OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FStalking Protection Orders ` which can
OL,7,Fban stalkers from going within a
OL,8,Fcertain distance of their victims, or
OL,9,Fcontacting them ` will also be made
OL,10,Fmore widely available, the Home Office
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe new approach will see courts able
OL,14,Fto impose such orders after a
OL,15,Fconviction even where none was in
OL,16,Fplace before a trial, contrary to the
OL,17,Fcurrent process where one has to have
OL,18,Fbeen in place already.
