OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FMs Cooper said: "Stalking is a
OL,7,Fhorrendous crime. For far too long,
OL,8,Fvictims of stalking have been subject
OL,9,Fto debilitating and vicious abuse at
OL,10,Fthe hands of stalkers who use any
OL,11,Fmeans necessary to monitor and control
OL,12,Ftheir victims' lives.
OL,14,F"Let us be clear, we will use every
OL,15,Ftool available to us to give more
OL,16,Fpower to victims and take it away from
OL,17,Fthe hands of their abusers.
