OL,6,FShe said: "I welcome today's
OL,7,Fannouncement which outlines a set of
OL,8,Fmeasures that will help towards
OL,9,Frectifying this. I am delighted that
OL,10,Fthe Government has agreed to review
OL,11,Fthe current stalking legislation and
OL,12,Fto increase the use of Stalking
OL,13,FProtection Orders, both of which I
OL,14,Fcalled for following my London
OL,15,FStalking Review.
