OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,F"Too often, I hear from victims facing
OL,7,Frelentless, terrifying behaviour from
OL,8,Fstalkers, only for the police or CPS
OL,9,Fto downgrade it to a lesser offence,
OL,10,Fsuch as malicious communications or
OL,11,Fharassment.
OL,13,F"It is clear the current stalking laws
OL,14,Fare failing to protect victims and I
OL,15,Furge Government to now proceed swiftly
OL,16,Fwith their review in this area."
