OL,3,CMore protection for victims as
OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FThe complaint ` made through a process
OL,7,Fwhich allows charities and other
OL,8,Fbodies to raise widespread problems
OL,9,Fwhich could affect public confidence
OL,10,Fin policing ` set out concerns
OL,11,Fincluding how there had been flawed
OL,12,Finvestigations, instances where
OL,13,Fstalking was not being properly
OL,14,Fidentified, officers "minimising or
OL,15,Ftrivialising" such behaviour and the
OL,16,Frisk of victims being seriously hurt
OL,17,For killed not being recognised.
OL,19,FThe Government has committed to
OL,20,Faccepting or partially accepting all
OL,21,Fof the recommendations.
