OL,4,CGovernment vows crackdown on stalking
OL,6,FThe IOPC welcomed action being taken
OL,7,Fto address the issues identified
OL,8,Fduring that joint investigation.
OL,10,FIts director general Rachel Watson
OL,11,Fsaid: "Change is happening and we
OL,12,Fwelcome the actions announced, which
OL,13,Fwill help to make a real difference to
OL,14,Fthose affected by this awful crime.
OL,16,F"In the new year, we will be
OL,17,Fpublishing all the responses we have
OL,18,Freceived to our recommendations, which
OL,19,Fwill outline more of the steps being
OL,20,Ftaken across policing to address this
OL,21,Fimportant issue."
